+-----------------------------------+
|  'Compact Menu 2' project README  |
+-----------------------------------+

== Summary

This project contains 'Compact Menu 2' add-on for Firefox, Thunderbird, Sunbird and SeaMonkey.


== Web links

Firefox Add-ons: https://addons.mozilla.org/firefox/addon/4550


== Build package

Require 'Apache Ant'.

$ tar zxf compact_menu_2.tar.gz
$ cd compact_menu_2
$ ant

== Import locales from Babelzilla

Require account of babelzilla.org.

$ export BABELZILLA_USER=user
$ export BABELZILLA_PASS=pass
$ ./update-locales.sh
